    <title>Linux防火墙命令速记</title>
    <url>/2023/05/01/1-%E8%BF%90%E7%BB%B4%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF/story2/Linux%E9%98%B2%E7%81%AB%E5%A2%99%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E9%80%9F%E8%AE%B0/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p><font color="orange" face="kaiti">防火墙相关</font></p>
<h2 id="查询有哪些端口是开启的"><a href="#查询有哪些端口是开启的" class="headerlink" title="查询有哪些端口是开启的"></a>查询有哪些端口是开启的</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">firewall-cmd --list-port</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="查询9090端口是否开启："><a href="#查询9090端口是否开启：" class="headerlink" title="查询9090端口是否开启："></a>查询9090端口是否开启：</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">firewall-cmd --query-port=9090/tcp</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="开启9090端口"><a href="#开启9090端口" class="headerlink" title="开启9090端口"></a>开启9090端口</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">firewall-cmd --zone=public --add-port=9090/tcp --permanent</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="重启防火墙生效"><a href="#重启防火墙生效" class="headerlink" title="重启防火墙生效"></a>重启防火墙生效</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">firewall-cmd --reload</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>命令含义：<br>–zone #作用域<br>–add-port&#x3D;9090&#x2F;tcp #添加端口，格式为：端口&#x2F;通讯协议<br>–permanent #永久生效，没有此参数重启后失效</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="删除9090端口"><a href="#删除9090端口" class="headerlink" title="删除9090端口"></a>删除9090端口</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">firewall-cmd --zone=public --remove-port=9090/tcp --permanent</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="重启防火墙生效-1"><a href="#重启防火墙生效-1" class="headerlink" title="重启防火墙生效"></a>重启防火墙生效</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">firewall-cmd --reload</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="关闭并禁用"><a href="#关闭并禁用" class="headerlink" title="关闭并禁用"></a>关闭并禁用</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl stop firewalld</span><br><span class="line">systemctl disable firewalld</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<br>

